You are right, there is an underlying problem.

Test is being disabled to unblock developers until it is fixed.
LGTM, and if I'm not around any other committer should feel to merge once tests are green.
I'm missing how the failing test is blocking developers - if the code under test is broken, shouldn't the test keep failing until new code is checked in, at which point the test will start passing?
